<del rend="strikethrough">die ſc </del> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>Mıchael<ex>is</ex></expan> . x<hi rend="sup">o</hi> . </ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula"><ab facs="#facs_165_r2l15"><expan>Ced<ex>u</ex>la</expan> </ab><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_165_r2l16">Auch <expan>lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde / Jſt bey vns geweſen / Dıetrich von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weite<ex>n</ex>mül</expan> </ab>
