<ab>Ulme, <expan>Nordling<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde, uns ist
                                <add><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Frankf<ex>ur</ex>t</expan></add> als
                            <expan>gest<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vier or auf den tage ein
                            <add>offen</add> brief kumen von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> erczbyschof von
                        Triere, herczog <expan>Ludwig<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>b<ex>ur</ex>ggraf<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Fridreich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. So ist uns auf hewt drey or auf den tag
                        ein <add>beslozzner</add> brief von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meincz <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>, der
                        beder wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> frewntschaft abschrifte schicken,
                                <expan>beslozze<ex>n</ex></expan> in disem briefe, daz sich ewr
                        weisheit darnach auch <expan>cze richt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wisse.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan> in <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Michael<ex>is</ex></expan> x<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula">
<ab><expan>Ced<ex>u</ex>la</expan>
<lb/>Auch, <add><expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan></add>, <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir ewr <expan>fruntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>, ob ir iht trefflichs west
                                    <add><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> den lewffen
                                    <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan></add>, daz ew füglich
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>cze schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz ir uns das bey
                                <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet. </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>Nördling<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> et <expan>ite<ex>rum</ex></expan>
                            ced<ex>u</ex>la<ex>m</ex>
<expan>ill<ex>is</ex></expan> de <expan>Nördling<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>t<ex>a</ex>m</expan>. </ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula">
<ab>Auch, <expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns nehst
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> het von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> müncze <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, davon
                                <expan>künne<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ew als
                                <expan>eigentlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> nicht
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>;
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wer etwer <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hie, der des von <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> begert, <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> etwas
                                <expan>müntlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> da von sagen, fürbas an ewr
                        weisheit cze bringen.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
